Package com.pizzeria.training.models

Enum Toppings

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Toppings>
com.pizzeria.training.models.Toppings
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Toppings>, java.lang.constant.Constable
public enum Toppings
extends java.lang.Enum<Toppings>
Enum for toppings to be put on a a pizza. Includes information for cost, as well as boolean flags for meat/vegan categories.
